{"TopicId":202636,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Few questions about KSP2","CreatedByName":"ErCos","CreatedById":210076,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T06:51:49Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ErCos","CreatedById":210076,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T06:51:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, devs. Do you have a plan to add a different types of weather on a planets with atmosphere (like rains or sandstorm)? And will kerbals need a protection of solar and space radiation for interplanetary flight, and can they get older or even...dead by radiation, dehydration, from old age etc? Will you add a food plants and toilets?\u00A0Do you going to add an inclination of planet\u0027s axis? And another question, you said that you do not add concept of randomly broked parts in a flight, but what else can do the game more challenging? I think that it is important part of any mission, when you need to develop a maximum reliable system that can live many years of flight, parts that \u00A0repaired by engineer can have a differnt more messy structure and it\u0027s very interesting looks and also realistic ( remember how many problems people have with a space stations in a real life because space station it is not a 2-hours flight to the Moon, it is a system that stay in orbit for years). Just think about it...\u003Cbr\u003E\nP.S. Sorry if you see many mistakes, I\u0027m from Ukraine =)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-24T07:30:24Z\u0022 title=\u002205/24/2021 07:30  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 24, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by ErCos\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Efixes and additions, but this was the last time, honestly\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T17:35:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/210076-ercos/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022210076\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/210076-ercos/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ErCos\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0 It hasn\u0027t been confirmed\u00A0yet weather planets with a atmosphere will have weather or not.\u00A0 It also have not been confirmed\u00A0weather Kerbals\u00A0will need life support like need. Like radiation protection, dehydration, and etcetera. And everything hasn\u0027t been confirmed yet. But I can tell you that more features will be added. I would refer\u00A0to the Show and Tell videos, the KSP2 episodes, and the Dev Dairies for more information.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat question though.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-24T17:36:22Z\u0022 title=\u002205/24/2021 05:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 24, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Dr. Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ESpelling and grammar. My autocorrect is a bit buggy.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T19:14:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621839109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have a plan to add a different types of weather on a planets with atmosphere (like rains or sandstorm)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo far there is only speculation. Some atmospherics have been confirmed (such as clouds)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621839109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd will kerbals need a protection of solar and space radiation for interplanetary flight, and can they get older or even...dead by radiation, dehydration, from old age etc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile we have no answer yet, the things we\u0027ve seen seem to imply that there will be radiation. Possibly even life support and aging\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621839109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill you add a food plants and toilets?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are greenhouses in the bases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621839109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you going to add an inclination of planet\u0027s axis?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI may be wrong but I thought this was confirmed. Can someone fact check me? I think Ovin is supposed to have an inclination and they showed us this in the first Friday show and tell.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621839109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. Sorry if you see many mistakes, I\u0027m from Ukraine =)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t worry, your english is great! Welcome to the forums!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207217-dr-kerbal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022207217\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207217-dr-kerbal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dr. Kerbal\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0said, for more info read the dev diaries and the KSP2 forum. Don\u0027t hesitate to ask questions and get clarifying info!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T19:38:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978134\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621883689\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204357\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerminator K-100\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Kerminator K-100 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI may be wrong but I thought this was confirmed. Can someone fact check me? I think Ovin is supposed to have an inclination and they showed us this in the first Friday show and tell.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYa. This one was actually confirmed. Planets will tilt to simulate seasons.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978134\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621883689\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204357\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerminator K-100\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Kerminator K-100 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are greenhouses in the bases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis have also been confirmed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ErCos","CreatedById":210076,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T19:55:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, thanks, guys. Yes, of course, I\u0027m checking all the stuff that show devs,\u00A0 but something I miss... thanks for your welcome btw!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbex","CreatedById":193998,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T20:15:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m only guessing but KSP2 isn\u0027t going to wipe out the modding community, so if it isn\u0027t in the game itself it\u0027ll likely be able to be modded in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ErCos","CreatedById":210076,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T20:26:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen will be cool if they add a in-game interface that make my life easier to download and update mods... also interested, how do you think, they will add a different towns and cities to Kerbal?\u00A0How long I can\u00A0speculate on this topic, would rather wait for the game itself \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T20:53:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8164423982\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/199981-kerbal-space-program-2-knowledge-repository/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a condensed heap of (nearly) everything that has been confirmed so far. Just in case.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PlutoISaPlanet","CreatedById":206057,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T21:16:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621887347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193998\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kerbex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m only guessing but KSP2 isn\u0027t going to wipe out the modding community, so if it isn\u0027t in the game itself it\u0027ll likely be able to be modded in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-25T00:18:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621887347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193998\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Kerbex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m only guessing but KSP2 isn\u0027t going to wipe out the modding community, so if it isn\u0027t in the game itself it\u0027ll likely be able to be modded in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can tell you this \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193998-kerbex/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022193998\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193998-kerbex/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kerbex\u003C/a\u003E. I dont think the modding community will die. I think it will boom and reach an all time high. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022205123\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Nate Simpson\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0himself said the game will be highly modable.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621887975\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210076\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ErCos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, ErCos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen will be cool if they add a in-game interface that make my life easier to download and update mods... also interested, how do you think, they will add a different towns and cities to Kerbal?\u00A0How long I can\u00A0speculate on this topic, would rather wait for the game itself \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be cool if the game had a mod maker in it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-25T18:24:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978285\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621901915\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dr. Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Dr. Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be cool if the game had a mod maker in it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr at least a better way to be able to make parts. Right now you have to load KSP every time you want to see the changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}